Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the control flow of the IBM_vpc-flowlogs-log-analysis system:

```plantuml
@startuml IBM_vpc-flowlogs-log-analysis

participant "COS Trigger" as COS
participant "Handler Function" as Handler
participant "COS Receiver Bucket" as ReceiverBucket
participant "COS Archive Bucket" as ArchiveBucket
participant "IBM Log Analysis" as LogAnalysis

COS -> Handler: Trigger (new log file)
activate Handler

Handler -> ReceiverBucket: Retrieve compressed log
ReceiverBucket --> Handler: Return compressed log

Handler -> Handler: Decompress log

Handler -> Handler: Parse JSON data

Handler -> Handler: Transform data

Handler -> LogAnalysis: Forward processed logs
activate LogAnalysis

alt Successful forwarding
    LogAnalysis --> Handler: Confirm receipt
else Error
    LogAnalysis --> Handler: Error response
    Handler -> Handler: Retry (up to 3 times)
end

deactivate LogAnalysis

Handler -> ArchiveBucket: Copy processed logs
ArchiveBucket --> Handler: Confirm copy

Handler -> ReceiverBucket: Delete original log
ReceiverBucket --> Handler: Confirm deletion

deactivate Handler

@enduml
```